GLOBAL FOLDER

USAGE NOTE:
FOR DEDICATED PROGRAMS, USE 'CopyVar' on your Homescreen or [VAR-LINk] menu TO IMPORT THE LIBRARY FROM THE /Main INTO YOUR /AppFolder, LIKE 'Import' IN PYTHON OR '#Include' IN C.

(The more experienced ones will definitely do a boot sequence.)

FnCheck :
---------
- Find out available locations, before using 'Define'.

Fncheck_lite : ( For dedicated Prgm )
--------------
- Also to Find out available locations before using 'Define'. (FUNCTION only)

InStrng2 :
----------
- Read a string content.
- To develop a text-based command assistant,
- or running a custom font,

ScnDtect :
----------
- Detect the screen configuration.

InitScrn :
----------
- Prepare your screen to PxlMode & restore
( Compatible 89, Titanium, 92, 92+ & V200 )

LoadScrn : ( ScnDtect required )
----------
- A simple LoadScreen.
( Compatible 89, Titanium, 92, 92+ & V200 )

MainClnr:
---------
- initializes essential variables needed for formal calculation.
